# IsToday(datetime)
- IF: ${ date(datetime) == date(ConvertToTZ(utcNow())) }
    - ${bool(true)}
- ELSE:
    - ${bool(false)}

# ConvertToTZ(datetime)
- ${convertFromUTC(formatDateTime(datetime), user.settings.mailboxSettings.timeZone)}

# GetLocation(event)
- IF: ${(event.location != null && event.location != '') && event.isOnlineMeeting == true }
    - ${ event.location }, [Microsoft Teams](${ event.onlineMeeting.joinUrl })
- ELSEIF: ${event.location != null && event.location != ''}
    - ${ event.location }
- ELSEIF: ${ event.isOnlineMeeting == true }
    - [Microsoft Teams](${ event.onlineMeeting.joinUrl })
- ELSE:
    - No location specified.